# ============================================
# PhishGuard Environment Variables
# ============================================

# ============================================
# REQUIRED - Application will not run without these
# ============================================

# Neon PostgreSQL Database Connection
# Get from: https://neon.tech (FREE)
# 1. Create account at neon.tech
# 2. Create new project
# 3. Copy connection string (includes username, password, host)
# 4. Paste here - MUST include ?sslmode=require at the end
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://username:password@ep-xxxxx.region.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require"

# Application URL
# Local: http://localhost:3000
# Vercel: https://your-app-name.vercel.app (update after first deploy)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"

# ============================================
# OPTIONAL - Advanced Scanning Features
# App works without these, but adds enhanced capabilities
# ============================================

# VirusTotal API Key (OPTIONAL)
# Purpose: Multi-engine malware scanning (60+ antivirus engines)
# Get from: https://www.virustotal.com/gui/join-us (FREE)
# Free tier: 500 lookups/day, 4 requests/minute
# Without this: Uses built-in single-engine file scanning
# VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY="your-virustotal-api-key-here"

# Google Safe Browsing API Key (OPTIONAL)
# Purpose: URL reputation checking against Google's threat database
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com (FREE)
# 1. Create project in Google Cloud Console
# 2. Enable "Safe Browsing API"
# 3. Create API key in Credentials
# Free tier: 10,000 queries/day
# Without this: Uses built-in pattern-based URL analysis
# GOOGLE_SAFE_BROWSING_API_KEY="your-google-api-key-here"

# OpenAI API Key (OPTIONAL)
# Purpose: AI-powered security chatbot (AI Assistant tab)
# Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# New accounts get $5 free credit
# Cost: ~$0.03 per 1K input tokens, ~$0.06 per 1K output tokens
# Without this: AI Assistant tab will be disabled
# OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-proj-your-openai-key-here"

# ============================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================

# 1. MINIMUM SETUP (Required):
#    - Copy this file to .env.local
#    - Add your Neon DATABASE_URL
#    - Set NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL to http://localhost:3000
#    - Run: npx prisma generate && npx prisma db push && npm run dev

# 2. FULL SETUP (All Features):
#    - Complete minimum setup above
#    - Uncomment and add VirusTotal API key (optional)
#    - Uncomment and add Google Safe Browsing API key (optional)
#    - Uncomment and add OpenAI API key (optional)
#    - Restart dev server

# 3. VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
#    - Add all environment variables in Vercel dashboard
#    - After first deploy, update NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL to your Vercel URL
#    - Redeploy to apply changes

