# ============================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ============================================

# ⚠️ NEVER commit .env.local to Git (it's in .gitignore)
# ⚠️ Use different API keys for development and production
# ⚠️ Rotate API keys periodically for security
# ⚠️ For production, use Vercel environment variables (not .env.local)
# ⚠️ Keep your DATABASE_URL secret - it has full database access

# ============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================

# Issue: "Cannot connect to database"
# Solution: Check DATABASE_URL has ?sslmode=require at the end

# Issue: "VirusTotal rate limit exceeded"
# Solution: Free tier is 500/day - upgrade or use built-in scanning

# Issue: "OpenAI API error"
# Solution: Check you have credits remaining at platform.openai.com/usage

# Issue: "NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL incorrect"
# Solution: For Vercel, update to your actual Vercel URL after first deploy

